  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110131123555\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110131123555\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p>몇일 전. </p>\r\n<p>퇴근했더니 </p>\r\n<p>가족들이 어서와서 이것 좀 보라고 호들갑!!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>가서 보니 둘째가 그림을 많~이 그렸더군요</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_267/isuhani_1328865000720C7YzO_JPEG/IMG_2209.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20120210_267/isuhani_1328865000720C7YzO_JPEG/IMG_2209.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A4539563')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_267/isuhani_1328865000720C7YzO_JPEG/IMG_2209.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>이 그림은 연필로.. 습작인 듯 하네요. </p>\r\n<p>동그란 얼굴, 눈, 코, 입.. 그리고 머리카락까지.</p>\r\n<p>있을 건 다 있네요</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_245/isuhani_13288650011007Es29_JPEG/IMG_2210.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20120210_245/isuhani_13288650011007Es29_JPEG/IMG_2210.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A4539563')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_245/isuhani_13288650011007Es29_JPEG/IMG_2210.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>이 그림은 윗 그림보다 더 초기 작품인가 봅니다.. 연습작.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_298/isuhani_1328865001844FInrq_JPEG/IMG_2207.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20120210_298/isuhani_1328865001844FInrq_JPEG/IMG_2207.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A4539563')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_298/isuhani_1328865001844FInrq_JPEG/IMG_2207.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>이 그림은 뭘 그린거야???</p>\r\n<p>사자!</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_51/isuhani_1328865001383uUxck_JPEG/IMG_2206.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20120210_51/isuhani_1328865001383uUxck_JPEG/IMG_2206.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A4539563')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_51/isuhani_1328865001383uUxck_JPEG/IMG_2206.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>얼굴만 그리지 말고 목도 그려봐 했더니.. 목과 몸통도 그렸네요..</p>\r\n<p>중간중간 얼룩무늬까지</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_232/isuhani_1328865002236TyIQw_JPEG/IMG_2208.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20120210_232/isuhani_1328865002236TyIQw_JPEG/IMG_2208.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A4539563')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_232/isuhani_1328865002236TyIQw_JPEG/IMG_2208.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>이건 뭘 그린거야?</p>\r\n<p>코끼리!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_156/isuhani_1328865002627X3LYi_JPEG/IMG_2211.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20120210_156/isuhani_1328865002627X3LYi_JPEG/IMG_2211.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A4539563')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_156/isuhani_1328865002627X3LYi_JPEG/IMG_2211.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>여기엔.. 턱수염까지 풍성하게 그려놨군요</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_154/isuhani_1328865002971Gcx1h_JPEG/IMG_2212.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20120210_154/isuhani_1328865002971Gcx1h_JPEG/IMG_2212.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A4539563')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_154/isuhani_1328865002971Gcx1h_JPEG/IMG_2212.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>이 그림도 디테일이 약한것이.. </p>\r\n<p>초기 작품인듯 합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_116/isuhani_1328865003410y4QFa_JPEG/IMG_1866.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20120210_116/isuhani_1328865003410y4QFa_JPEG/IMG_1866.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A4539563')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20120210_116/isuhani_1328865003410y4QFa_JPEG/IMG_1866.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>그림을 그린 주인공.</p>\r\n<p>둘째아이.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>보이시 하지만.. 딸이랍니다 </p>\r\n<p>지금 25개월이죠 ^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
